OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1772204159
OL,3,CMan jailed after strapping hoax bomb
OL,4,Cto post outside shop
OL,6,FA man who strapped a hoax bomb to a
OL,7,Fpost outside a shop in Gateshead has
OL,8,Fbeen jailed.
OL,10,FJohn Maughan, now aged 50, strapped
OL,11,Fthe device, which had a clock, to a
OL,12,Fmetal post near the Nisa Local shop in
OL,13,FDurham Road, Birtley.
OL,15,FPolice were alerted just before 8.30am
OL,16,Fon Monday, 17 November and they
OL,17,Fattended, putting a cordon in place
OL,18,Fand evacuating a number of properties
OL,19,Fin the area.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/4
