FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1772204159
OL,3,CMan jailed after strapping hoax bomb
OL,4,Cto post outside shop
OL,6,FThe Explosive Ordnance Disposal (EOD)
OL,7,Fteam attended the scene to carry out
OL,8,Fenquiries into the package, which was
OL,9,Fconfirmed to not pose a risk to the
OL,10,Fpublic and was subsequently confirmed
OL,11,Fas a hoax bomb.
OL,13,FJohn Maughan, from Morpeth, was
OL,14,Farrested at an address on Eslington
OL,15,FTerrace in Newcastle on suspicion of
OL,16,Fplacing a hoax bomb with intent.
OL,18,FHe initially pleaded not guilty and
OL,19,Fwas due to stand trial but admitted
OL,20,Fthe charge in January.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
