OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1772204159
OL,3,CMan jailed after strapping hoax bomb
OL,4,Cto post outside shop
OL,6,FOn Wednesday 25 February, he was
OL,7,Fsentenced to 16 months behind bars at
OL,8,FNewcastle Crown Court.
OL,10,FDetective Constable Chester Dixon, the
OL,11,Fofficer in charge of the case, said:
OL,12,F"Maughan's actions that day was an
OL,13,Fincredibly reckless and disruptive act
OL,14,Fcarried out with absolutely no regard
OL,15,Ffor the fear it would cause within the
OL,16,Fcommunity.
OL,18,F"While Maughan initially tried to
OL,19,Fsuggest the device was 'just a joke',
OL,20,Factions like this are no laughing
OL,21,Fmatter.
OL,26,@tD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/4
