PN,42104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1772204159
OL,3,CMan jailed after strapping hoax bomb
OL,4,Cto post outside shop
OL,6,F"The presence of a suspected device
OL,7,Fquite understandably alarmed residents
OL,8,Fand required a significant emergency
OL,9,Fresponse to ensure everyone's safety."
OL,11,FHe added: "I hope today's outcome
OL,12,Freassures the public that we will take
OL,13,Frobust action against anyone who seeks
OL,14,Fto cause unnecessary panic or waste
OL,15,Fvaluable emergency resources."
